content: Kira actually 136,629,046 votes for President were cast: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/u/1/d/133Eb4qQmOxNvtesw2hdVns073R68EZx4SfCnP4IGQf8/htmlview?sle=true#gid=19 This does not include blank votes for President where voters voted for other things Down Ballot. In California only 14,181,595 people voted for President but 14,610,509 cast ballots : http://elections.cdn.sos.ca.gov/sov/2016-general/sov/2016-complete-sov.pdf . Hope this helps.
